<li id="cite_note-90"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-90">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFHesselink2004">Hesselink 2004</a>, p.&#160;85; <a href="#CITEREFParker1995">Parker 1995</a>, p.&#160;43</span>
